Invocation Name: dogpatch solutions tracker
des:
The purpose of this skill is to record neighborhood problems in Dogpatch neighborhood of San Francisco, California, USA. This skill allows users to report neighborhood issues such as potholes, graffiti, trash, debris, encampments etc to Dogpatch Solutions Tracker.

A local patrol is dispatched to ascertain the validity of the issue. If the issue is valid, it is then reported at : https://dogpatch.solutionstracker.org/map and its resolution tracked.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
